                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A4e/552: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Delegation</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-02-01T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1926—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>11. Position outlined in your Conference Number 24, January 30, 5 p.m., has the
                    approval of the Department.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
